			  <h3>The Story</h3>
				<div class="para">
			  Stalkninja is a result of talks with startups and SME who frequently need tech hand for their small tech jobs. While intern model works for lot of them, it does not work round the year. On the other hand, lot of college students have started freelancing with various companies on regular basis. Stalk Ninja is an attempt to provide one stop solution to connect the two segments.
				<br/><br/>
				It is also an attempt to show-case the motivated & hands on student developers from across the nation. The vision is to be a linkedin of student developers where the potential employers can see the past performance of the Ninjas. The profile of the Ninja would act as his online resume with credible information.
